Package: cockpit-bin
Section: libs
Architecture: linux-any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, xdg-utils
Description: desktop shortcut for accessing cockpit
 Cockpit runs in a browser and can manage your network of GNU/Linux
 machines.

Package: cockpit-bridge
Section: libs
Architecture: linux-any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, policykit-1
Description: backend for web interface
 The Cockpit bridge component installed server side and runs commands on the
 system on behalf of the web based user interface.

Package: cockpit-doc
Section: doc
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: documentation - deployment and developer guide
 The Cockpit Deployment and Developer Guide shows sysadmins how to
 deploy Cockpit on their machines as well as helps developers who want to
 embed or extend Cockpit.

Package: cockpit-docker
Section: libs
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, docker.io (>= 1.3.0)
Description: docker integration for cockpit user interface
 The Cockpit components for interacting with Docker and user interface.
 This package is not yet complete.

